%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natural%20gas%20prices%20jump%20as%20Qatar%20says%20it%20is%20shutting%20down%20production%20after%20Iranian%20strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22qatarenergy%20logo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a58a711fb3fcb42648b6bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222857%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EArtur%20Widak%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20QatarEnergy%20said%20it%20ceased%20production%20at%20one%20of%20its%20energy%20facilities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProduction%20was%20paused%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20military%20attacks%26quot%3B%20on%20some%20of%20the%20company's%20operating%20facilities%2C%20QatarEnergy%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENatural%20gas%20prices%20jumped%20on%20Monday%2C%20as%20did%20other%20energy%20commodities%2C%20including%20crude%20oil.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EQatar's%20state-owned%20energy%20company%20has%20halted%20production%20of%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%2C%20LNG%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-companies-middle-east-employee-safety-iran-conflict-dubai-uae-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIranian%20drone%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20damaged%20one%20of%20its%20production%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20military%20attacks%20on%20QatarEnergy's%20operating%20facilities%20in%20Ras%20Laffan%20Industrial%20City%20and%20Mesaieed%20Industrial%20City%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Qatar%2C%20QatarEnergy%20has%20ceased%20production%20of%20liquefied%20natural%20gas%20(LNG)%20and%20associated%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20QatarEnergy%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENatural%20gas%20prices%20surged%20on%20Monday%2C%20with%20prices%20up%20more%20than%206%25%2C%20mirroring%20similar%20rises%20in%20other%20energy%20commodities.%20Brent%20crude%20oil%2C%20the%20international%20benchmark%2C%