20me%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20she%20struggled%20to%20get%20up%20from%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20patience%2C%20I%20guided%20her%20through%20the%20steps%20until%20she%20could%20do%20it%20herself.%20After%20over%2030%20years%20of%20training%20together%2C%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20times%20I%20consciously%20thought%20about%20how%20her%20movements%20have%20changed%20as%20she's%20aged%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20how%20I%20want%20to%20age%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20shown%20me%20that%20she%20can%20be%20disciplined%20and%20committed%20to%20her%20health%20while%20still%20enjoying%20life%2C%20reinforcing%20my%20belief%20that%20mindset%20shapes%20how%20we%20age%20just%20as%20much%20as%20movement%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20working%20out%20with%20her%20has%20shaped%20the%20way%20I%20view%20aging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214458cc4-34fa-41f9-81cd-568ccdbabe2c%5C%22%3EShe's%20taught%20me%20that%20health%20is%20a%20lifelong%20commitment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20before%20I%20created%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjanetosbornefitness.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanet%20Osborne%20Fitness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20online%20fitness%20platform%20for%20all%20ages%2C%20or%20included%20my%20mom%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjanetosbornefitness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstagram%20videos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20regularly%20exercised%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20was%2034%20and%20working%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foptimize-workout-personal-trainer-red-green-flags-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epersonal%20trainer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20told%20me%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20strong%20and%20independent%20as%20she%20aged%2C%20so%20I%20made%20her%20a%2030-minute%20step-and-strength%20workout%20video.%20She%20consistently%20did%20it%20five%20days%20each%20week%2C%20inspiring%20me%20to%20create%20new%20programs%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20either%20of%20us%20realizing%20it%2C%20this%20routine%20had%20become%20a%20meaningful%20part%20of%20our%20relationship.%20It%20gave%20us%20a%20reason%20to%20talk%2C%20check%20in%20with%20each%20other%2C%20and%20share%20something%20uniquely%20ours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20she's%2087%20and%20focused%20on%20longevity%2C%20I%20tailor%20her%20plan%20to%20prioritize%20strength%2C%20balance%2C%20mobility%2C%20and%20stretching%20so%20she%20can%20complete%20everyday%20tasks%20like%20getting%20in%20and%20out%20of%20a%20chair%2C%20walking%20up%20the%20stairs%2C%20opening%20heavy%20doors%2C%20carrying%20groceries%2C%20and%20even%20getting%20up%20from%20the%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22965b9d31-8553-4e72-8223-2cad1ab91485%5C%22%3EOur%20workouts%20have%20made%20me%20slow%20down%20and%20value%20modifications%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222654%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Janet%20Osborne%20and%20get%20mother%20standing%20side%20by%20side%20on%20golf%20course%20holding%20golf%20clubs%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6992f518e1ba468a96ac1f0f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221991%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20try%20to%20take%20our%20movements%20outdoors%20whenever%20we%20can.%3Cp%3EJanet%20Osborne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETraining%20an%2087-year-old%20has%20taught%20me%20to%20meet%20her%20right%20where%20she%20is.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20offer%20modifications%2C%20guiding%20her%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-things-that-improve-workouts-reddit-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslow%20and%20small%20movements%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20example%2C%20overhead%20presses%20aren't%20comfortable%20for%20her%2C%20so%20she%20does%20front%20raises%20and%20lateral%20lifts%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20practices%20exercises%20between%20sessions%20to%20improve%20her%20form%20and%20then%20shows%20off%20her%20progress%20the%20next%20time%20I%20see%20her.%20After%20habitually%20practicing%20single-leg%20stands%2C%20she%20went%20from%20needing%20wall%20support%20to%20balance%20on%20one%20leg%20for%2010%20seconds%20to%20standing%20unsupported%20on%20one%20leg%20for%2040%20seconds%20straight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn't%20always%20stack%20all%20of%20the%20moves%20in%20one%20long%20workout.%20I've%20noticed%20that%20she%20sprinkles%20movement%20throughout%20her%20day%2C%20whether%20she%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-tests-show-how-well-aging-do-now-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20tests%20her%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20waiting%20for%20the%20elevator%2C%20squeezes%20in%20some%20calf%20raises%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20or%20pauses%20for%20a%20mobility%20break%20on%20her%20walk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20my%20classes%20were%20very%20intense%20and%20lasted%20at%20least%20one%20hour%2C%20but%20working%20out%20with%20her%20has%20shown%20me%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudy-hiit-short-workouts-boost-fitness-longevity-stroke-survival-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshorter%20spurt%20of%20focused%20movement%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20also%20be%20effective.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20inspired%20me%20to%20go%20from%20chasing%20extremes%20and%20intensity%20to%20focusing%20on%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a28bfb4-e92d-4200-87da-ee26c69045b2%5C%22%3EShe%20reminds%20me%20to%20find%20joy%20in%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20work%20hard%20on%20our%20fitness%20without%20taking%20ourselves%20too%20seriously.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom%20occasionally%20mixes%20up%20her%20right%20and%20left%2C%20and%20we%20often%20freeze%20mid-movement%20and%20burst%20into%20giggles.%20Her%20sense%20of%20humor%20is%20one%20of%20her%20greatest%20strengths%2C%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20she's%20aging%20so%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20our%20workouts%2C%20I'll%20sometimes%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20smiling%2C%20Mom%3F%26quot%3B%20She'll%20reply%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20concentrating!%26quot%3B%20before%20breaking%20into%20a%20huge%20grin.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20moments%20%E2%80%94%20the%20laughing%2C%20gentle%20teasing%2C%20and%20shared%20pride%20%E2%80%94%20make%20every%20session%20feel%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2eac4af-7d32-4a82-a184-c546099032ba%5C%22%3EMy%20mom%20is%20consistent%20in%20her%20approach%20to%20health%20outside%20of%20the%20gym%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223812%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22janet%20osborne%20and%20her%20mother%20posing%20side%20by%20side%20on%20bridge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6992f5e6d3c7faef0ece5775%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222859%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20mom%20has%20been%20consistent%20in%20her%20approach%20to%20health%20since%20I%20was%20a%20child.%3Cp%3EJanet%20Osborne%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20diet%2C%20my%20mom%20prioritizes%20simplicity%2C%20and%20she's%20always%20been%20this%20way.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20raising%20me%2C%20she%20made%20%3Cem%3Eeverything%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20scratch%2C%20from%20doughnuts%20to%20shepherd's%20pie.%20She%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-start-growing-your-own-food-like-homesteaders-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrew%20vegetables%20in%20our%20backyard%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20built%20our%20meals%20around%20simple%2C%20whole%20foods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2087%2C%20she%20focuses%20on%20eating%20enough%20protein%2C%20getting%20plenty%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%2C%20and%20drinking%20green%20tea%20daily.%20She%20works%20to%20fuel%20her%20body%20in%20a%20way%20that%20supports%20her%20energy%20and%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%20Looking%20back%2C%20her%20instinctive%20approach%20to%20food%20is%20what%20sparked%20my%20own%20interest%20in%20nutrition%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20gotten%20older%2C%20I've%20come%20to%20see%20food%20as%20a%20powerful%20tool%20to%20embrace%20rather%20than%20something%20to%20restrict.%20She's%20proven%20that%20it%20can%20help%20keep%20a%20person%20feeling%20strong%2C%20energized%2C%20and%20independent%20as%20they%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d29dc33-c35b-4d5a-96b5-cbc277e0aac7%5C%22%3EExercising%20with%20her%20has%20shown%20me%20that%20aging%20can%20be%20active%20and%20connected%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20viewed%20my%20mother%20as%20an%20inspiration.%20Even%20so%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20deeply%20she%20inspired%20everyone%20else%20watching%20our%20workouts%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20our%20first%20video%20gained%20traction%2C%20people%20left%20comments%20saying%20they%20saw%20their%20own%20parents%2C%20grandparents%2C%20or%20older%20selves%20in%20her.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20said%20she%20gave%20them%20hope%3B%20others%20said%20she%20made%20them%20cry.%20Many%20told%20me%20they%20hadn't%20exercised%20in%20years%20but%20were%20going%20to%20try%20again%20because%20of%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20expect%20so%20many%20people%20to%20need%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffit-grandparents-motivation-exercise-busy-dad-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esomeone%20in%20their%2080s%20moving%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20laughing%2C%20modifying%2C%20and%20doing%20their%20best.%20She%20makes%20exercise%20feel%20possible%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking%20out%20with%20my%20mom%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20joys%20of%20my%20life.%20It%20brings%20us%20closer%2C%20keeps%20her%20moving%2C%20and%20reminds%20both%20of%20us%20that%20it's%20never%20too%20late%20to%20take%20care%20of%20our%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraining-elderly-mother-helped-aging-mentality-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fd