cials%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20is%20also%20staying%20close%20to%20clients%20in%20the%20region%20as%20the%20situation%20unfolds%20and%20has%20made%20safety%20a%20top%20priority%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ECitigroup%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fciti-jane-fraser-memo-old-habits-performance-job-cuts-transformation-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECitigroup%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20told%20its%20employees%20to%20work%20from%20home%20until%20further%20notice%2C%20a%20Citi%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20safety%20of%20our%20employees%20is%20our%20number%20one%20priority%2C%20and%20we%20are%20continuing%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20help%20keep%20our%20employees%20and%20their%20families%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20continuing%20to%20serve%20our%20clients%20and%20we%20have%20robust%20contingency%20and%20resilience%20plans%20in%20place%20for%20that%20purpose%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJPMorgan%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20has%20also%20advised%20its%20employees%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20region%20to%20work%20from%20home%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-tech-budget-ai-20-billion-jamie-dimon-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS's%20largest%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20offices%20in%20Abu%20Dhabi%20and%20Dubai%2C%20and%2C%20across%20the%20wider%20region%2C%20in%20Beirut%2C%20Cairo%2C%20Doha%2C%20Manama%2C%20and%20Riyadh.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20is%20assessing%20the%20situation%20regularly%20to%20adjust%20guidance%20as%20needed%2C%20the%20person%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EFedEx%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22FedEx%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a569231fb3fcb42648b572%3