r%20look%20at%20the%20projectile%20protruding%20from%20the%20fuselage%20of%20the%20fixed-wing%20heavy%20bomber%20revealed%20something%20far%20more%20improvised.%20The%20object%20was%20about%2060%20centimeters%20(roughly%20two%20feet)%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhotos%20that%20the%20unit%20shared%20exclusively%20with%20Business%20Insider%20show%20the%20trident%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221062%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20trident%20impaled%20in%20a%20Ukrainian%20drone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699d67a42237a6a8f0cdb708%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221416%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trident%20stuck%20in%20the%20fuselage%20of%20the%20Backfire%20drone.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alex%20Eine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22745%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20trident%20that%20was%20found%20in%20a%20Ukrainian%20bomber%20drone.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699d6cda156648bc16a8c666%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20trident%20is%20made%20of%20nails%20and%20steel%20rods.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Alex%20Eine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEine%20said%20that%20the%20unit%20is%20unsure%20exactly%20how%20or%20when%20the%20drone%20was%20struck%20during%20the%20mission.%20There%20are%20spots%20on%20a%20telemetry%20log%20that%20might%20mark%20the%20moment%20of%20impact%2C%20but%20wind%20gusts%20can%20have%20the%20same%20effect.%20It%20is%20ultimately%20inconclusive.%20Eine%20said%20they%20ruled%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-electronic-warfare-fight-drone-pilots-must-sort-safe-paths-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efriendly%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20possibility%20due%20to%20high%20levels%20of%20coordination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Backfire%20drone%20sustained%20some%20additional%20scratches%2C%20but%20overall%2C%20it%20mana