0hours%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Boeing%20787%20Dreamliner%20not%20only%20flew%20across%20the%20Atlantic%20but%20as%20far%20as%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea%2C%20before%20it%20U-turned%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Spain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20world%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevery-airline-flies-the-airbus-a380-and-their-destinations-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEmirates%20Airbus%20A380%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20off%20from%20Auckland%2C%20New%20Zealand%2C%20expecting%20a%2016-hour%20trip%20to%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20eight%20hours%20into%20the%20flight%2C%20the%20double-decker%20jet%20changed%20course%20%E2%80%94%20forced%20to%20double%20back%20over%20Australia%20and%20the%20Tasman%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20of%20the%20world%20shows%20the%20paths%20of%20two%20flights%20that%20U-turned%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20amid%20the%20conflict%20in%20Iran%2C%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20Doha%2C%20and%20Auckland%20to%20Dubai.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a56aaed3e2f1aef369c7ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222488%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20American%20Dreamliner%20landed%20back%20in%20Philadelphia%2015%20hours%20and%2032%20minutes%20after%20taking%20off%20from%20there%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20Flightradar24.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlight%20120%20was%20canceled%20over%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20too%2C%20while%20Qatari%20airspace%20remains%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Emirates%20A380%20returned%20to%20Auckland%20after%2015%20hours%20and%2037%20minutes%20in%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dubai-based%20airline%20usually%20operates%20some%20500%20flights%20a%20day%2C%20but%20UAE%20airspace%20has%20been%20closed%20since%20early%20Saturday.%20Dozens%20of%20Emirates'%20planes%20have%20been%20left%20in%20unexpected%20cities%20across%20the%20world%20after%20being%20forced%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-strikes-flight-diversions-map-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edivert%20en%20route%20to%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20incidents%20occurring%20in%20either%20hemisphere%20highlight%20just%20how%20important%20the%20Middle%20East%20is%20for%20aviation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20region's%20three%20major%20airlines%20%E2%80%94%20Qatar%20Airways%2C%20Emirates%2C%20and%20Etihad%20%E2%80%94%20operate%20huge%20hubs%20that%20connect%20passengers%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%20Its%20geography%20makes%20it%20a%20convenient%20stopover%20between%20Asia%20and%20Europe%2C%20or%20onward%20to%20North%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20airlines%20collectively%20carry%2090%2C000%20transiting%20passengers%20through%20their%20hubs%20daily%2C%20excluding%20those%20destined%20for%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20according%20to%20the%20aviation%20analytics%20firm%20Cirium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Persian%20Gulf%20is%20also%20a%20major%20flight%20corridor%20for%20aircraft%20that%20don't%20land%20there%2C%20such%20as%20flights%20from%20India%20or%20Australia%20to%20Europe.%20They%20have%20instead%20been%20rerouting%20over%20Saudi%20Arabia%20or%20the%20Caucasus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisruption%20to%20flights%20has%20hit%20airline%20stocks%2C%20with%20major%20carriers%20worldwide%20seeing%20sharp%20share%20price%20falls%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-conflict-triggers-2-of-longest-ever-flights-to-nowhere-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772450428000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a56a8a1fb3fcb42648b574%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-conflict-triggers-2-of-longest-ever-flights-to-nowhere-2026-