ts%20were%20mistakenly%20shot%20down%20by%20friendly%20fire%20during%20combat%20operations%20against%20Iran%2C%20US%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20F-15%20Strike%20Eagle%20takes%20off.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a52838d3e2f1aef369c6eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20F-15%20Strike%20Eagle%20was%20downed%20over%20Kuwait%20early%20on%20Monday%20local%20time.%3Cp%3EJason%20Wells%2FLoop%20Images%2FUniversal%20Images%20Group%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20says%20three%20of%20its%20aircraft%20have%20been%20downed%20over%20Kuwait%20and%20all%20crew%20are%20safe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20said%20three%20F-15Es%20went%20down%20over%20Kuwait%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20an%20apparent%20friendly%20fire%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESocial%20media%20footage%20appeared%20to%20show%20an%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagle%20falling%20in%20a%20tailspin%20near%20a%20US%20air%20base.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20said%20three%20of%20its%20military%20aircraft%20went%20down%20over%20Kuwait%2C%20marking%20the%20Pentagon's%20first%20known%20air%20assets%20downed%20during%20the%20US%20and%20Israel's%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-iran-israel-ayatollah-ali-khamenei-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewar%20with%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20said%20on%20Monday%20morning%20that%20at%2011%3A01%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20Sunday%2C%20%26quot%3Bthree%20U.S.%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagles%20flying%20in%20support%20of%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20went%20down%20over%20Kuwait%20due%20to%20an%20apparent%20friendly%20fire%20incident.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20active%20combat%20%E2%80%94%20that%20included%20attacks%20from%20Iranian%20aircraft%2C%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20and%20drones%20%E2%80%94%20the%20U.S.%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20jets%20were%20mistakenly%20shot%20down%20by%20Kuwaiti%20air%20defenses%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20all%20six%20of%20the%20aircrew%20ejected%20safely%20and%20were%20safely%20recovered%2C%20and%20are%20now%20in%20stable%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20incident%20is%20under%20investigation%20and%20more%20information%20would%20be%20released%20when%20it%20becomes%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKuwait%20has%20acknowledged%20this%20incident%2C%20and%20we%20are%20grateful%20for%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20Kuwaiti%20defense%20forces%20and%20their%20support%20in%20this%20ongoing%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Kuwaiti%20Army%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20US%20military%20aircraft%20crashed%20this%20morning%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20all%20crew%20members%20involved%20were%20safe%20and%20in%20stable%20condition.%20It%20did%20not%20give%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20crashes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecent%20social%20media%20footage%20showed%20a%20fighter%20aircraft%20resembling%20an%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagle%20falling%20to%20the%20ground%20in%20a%20tailspin.%20A%20separate%20clip%20appeared%20to%20show%20two%20parachutes%20descending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20could%20not%20independently%20verify%20when%20the%20footage%20was%20shot%2C%20but%20it%20corresponds%20visually%20to%20a%20location%20in%20Al%20Jahra%2C%20on%20the%20western%20outskirts%20of%20Kuwait%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20puts%20the%20crash%20site%20roughly%20six%20miles%20east%20of%20the%20Ali%20Al%20Salem%20US%20Air%20Base%2C%20which%20has%20been%20actively%20fending%20off%20hundreds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-damage-luxury-tourism-dubai-fairmont-palm-iran-airstrike-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIranian%20missile%20and%20drone%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20weekend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideos%20also%20showed%20two%20uniformed%20personnel%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20appearing%20to%20cautiously%20interact%20with%20civilians.%20Another%20clip%20appears%20to%20show%20a%20man%20wearing%20a%20flight%20helmet%20sitting%20in%20the%20trunk%20of%20a%20non-military%20hatchback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20detailed%20multiple%20friendly%20fire%20incidents%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20including%20a%20US%20Navy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnavy-warship-fired-at-us-fighter-jets-mistaken-enemy-missiles-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewarship%20firing%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20two%20American%20F%2FA-18%20fighter%20jets%20over%20the%20Red%20Sea%20in%202024.%20The%20crew%20safely%20ejected%2C%20and%20an%20investigation%20found%20that%20the%20ship's%20crew%20mistook%20the%20jets%20for%20anti-ship%20cruise%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Houthi%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20McDonnell%20Douglas%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagle%20is%20a%20twin-seat%20aircraft%20intended%20to%20be%20flown%20by%20a%20pilot%20and%20a%20weapons%20systems%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Air%20Force%20fields%20over%20400%20F-15%20Eagles%2C%20battle-proven%20multirole%20strike%20fighters%20that%20have%20been%20deployed%20in%20combat%20since%20the%20Gulf%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Central%20Command%20on%20Sunday%20listed%20many%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-us-combat-systems-first-day-iran-fight-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eassets%20that%20it%20brought%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20fight%2C%20including%20B-2%20Stealth%20Bombers%2C%20F-18%2C%20F-16%2C%20and%20F-22%20fighter%20jets%2C%20A-10%20attack%20jets%2C%20and%20F-35%20stealth%20fighters%2C%20along%20with%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20capabilities%20we%20can't%20list.%26quot%3B%20It%20did%20not%20list%20any%20variants%20of%20the%20F-15.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20US%20military%20said%20on%20Sunday%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-service-members-killed-wounded-fighting-iran-american-military-says-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20American%20service%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20killed%20and%20another%20five%20were%20seriously%20wounded%20amid%20the%20Pentagon's%20combat%20operations%20against%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20sadly%2C%20there%20will%20likely%20be%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20day.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20it%20ends.%20That's%20the%20way%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20Israel%20launched%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-hundreds-fighters-struck-iran-largest-ever-air-operation-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebarrage%20of%20strikes%20against%20Iran%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Saturday%2C%20killing%20the%20Iranian%20supreme%20leader%2C%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%2C%20and%20hitting%20over%202%2C000%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-losses-iran-israel-kuwait-several-warplanes-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772450192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a528fbd3e2f1aef369c6f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-losses-iran-israel-kuwait-several-warplanes-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Central%20Command%20said%20three%20U.S.%20F-15E%20Strike%20Eagles%20went%20down%20over%20Kuwait%20%26quot%3Bdue%20to%20an%20apparent%20friendly%20fire%20incident.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mloh%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Loh%2CSin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-aircraft-losses-iran-israel-kuwait-several-warplanes-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Large-scale%2C%20resource-intensive%2C%20and%20sustained'%3A%20OpenAI%20reveals%20China's%20operation%20to%20silence%20dissidents%20on%20social%20media%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20this%20photo%20illustration%20a%2014-year-old%20boy%20holds%20an%20iPhone%20screen%20displaying%20various%20social%20media%20and%20messaging%20apps%20on%20February%2023%2C%202026%20in%20Bath%2C%20England.%20On%20top%20row%20left%20to%20right%2C%20the%20logo%20of%20social%20media%20platform%20Instagram%20is%20seen%20beside%20that%20of%20Meta's%20Threads%20and%20Facebook.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fb0ea50f42603b0f8ee6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOpenAI%20publishes%20a%20report%20detailing%20China's%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20special%20operations%26quot%3B%20that%20target%20critics%20online.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Barclay%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20published%20a%20report%20detailing%20China's%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20special%20operations%26quot%3B%20that%20target%20critics%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20report%20followed%20OpenAI's%20findings%20and%20removal%20of%20a%20ChatGPT%20account%20belonging%20to%20the%20CCP.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBluesky%20said%20it%20recently%20removed%20a%20small%20number%20of%20accounts%20for%20%26quot%3Binauthentic%20coordinated%20activity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20that%20even%20the%20Chinese%20government%20uses%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20according%20to%20a%20cybersecurity%20report%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20how%20OpenAI%20uncovered%20China's%20%26quot%3Bcyber%20special%20operations%26quot%3B%20targeting%20political%20dissidents%20in%20China%20and%20abroad%2C%20after%20the%20company%20found%20and%20removed%20an%20account%20owned%20by%20the%20Chinese%20government%20that%20uploaded%20periodic%20status%20reports%20to%20ChatGPT%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20be%20polished.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20OpenAI's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-scams-security-report-chatgpt-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDisrupting%20Malicious%20Uses%20of%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20report%20published%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20third%20of%20the%20document%20detailed%20China's%20tactics%20to%20silence%20and%20intimidate%20critics%20across%20social%20media%20platforms%20owned%20by%20American%20tech%20giants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20effort%20appears%20to%20be%20large-scale%2C%20resource-intensive%20and%20sustained%2C%20counting%20at%20least%20hundreds%20of%20staff%2C%20thousands%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffake-twitter-accounts-elon-musk-x-location-2025-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBut%2520lots%2520of%2520other%2520people%2Cscrewing%2520around%2520on%2520social%2520media.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efake%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20across%20scores%20of%20platforms%2C%20the%20use%20of%20locally%20deployed%20AI%20models%2C%20and%20a%20playbook%20of%20dozens%20of%20tactics%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20targets%20are%20not%20just%20people%20in%20China%2C%20but%20also%20dissidents%20around%20the%20world%20and%20representatives%20of%20foreign%20countries%2C%20up%20to%20and%20including%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-election-result-debt-market-jgb-bond-yields-takaichi-trade-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprime%20minister%20of%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20report%20documented%20instances%20in%20which%20operatives%20for%20China%20forged%20US%20county%20court%20documents%20and%20submitted%20them%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20have%20certain%20posts%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20operatives%20with%20thousands%20of%20fake%20accounts%20also%20collectively%20submitted%20abusive%20reports%20on%20dissidents%20to%20social%20media%20platforms%20to%20intentionally%20trigger%20false%20account%20bans%20and%20content%20restrictions%2C%20according%20to%20OpenAI.%20Many%20of%20these%20false%20reports%2C%20OpenAI%20said%2C%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-small-business-owners-swamped-by-scammers-generative-ai-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20posing%20as%20screenshots%20of%20conversations%20and%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20largest%20accounts%20on%20X%20have%20been%20targeted%2C%20according%20to%20OpenAI.%20That%20includes%20the%20handle%20%40whyyoutouzhele%2C%20better%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BTeacher%20Li%20is%20not%20your%20teacher%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20the%20fifth-largest%20overall%20traffic%20share%20on%20X%20as%20of%20January%2C%20with%20more%20than%202.1%20million%20followers.%20The%20account%20mainly%20posts%20videos%20from%20inside%20China%2C%20often%20documenting%20instances%20of%20corruption%20and%20human%20rights%20abuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20social%20platforms%20like%20X%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Bluesky%20realize%20that%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-says-online-harassment-is-up-after-content-moderation-changes-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtent%20moderation%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20being%20used%20by%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20as%20a%20weapon%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20behind%20the%20Teacher%20Li%20account%20wrote%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20call%20on%20the%20entire%20AI%20industry%20to%20take%20this%20matter%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20team%20added%20in%20the%20original%20post%20written%20in%20Chinese.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20your%20technology%20is%20being%20used%20to%20systematically%20oppress%20human%20rights%2C%20to%20say%20that%20'we're%20just%20makers%20of%20a%20tool'%20is%20not%20an%20acceptable%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20social%20media%20platforms%20have%20observed%20similar%20patterns%20and%20have%20taken%20action%20to%20curb%20these%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Rodericks%2C%20head%20of%20trust%20and%20safety%20at%20Bluesky%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20platform%20has%20invested%20in%20its%20capabilities%20to%20identify%20and%20disrupt%20influence%20operations%20like%20those%20described%20in%20the%20OpenAI%20report%2C%20including%20hiring%20specialized%20investigative%20staff%20and%20expanding%20monitoring%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20part%20of%20this%20ongoing%20work%2C%20the%20team%20recently%20removed%20a%20small%20number%20of%20accounts%2C%20consistent%20with%20those%20described%20in%20the%20report%2C%20that%20were%20engaged%20in%20inauthentic%20coordinated%20activity%20in%20violation%20of%20our%20Community%20Guidelines%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rodericks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20person%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Meta%20includes%20activities%20that%20OpenAI%20described%20in%20its%20regular%20adversarial%20report%2C%20and%20takes%20action%20against%20accounts%20found%20to%20be%20violating%20platform%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20and%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-reveals-chinas-large-scale-effort-to-silence-dissidents-online-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772450101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F699fb5bc1fb3fcb426487ad1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-reveals-chinas-large-scale-effort-to-silence-dissidents-online-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Chinese%20government's%20ChatGPT%20usage%20reveals%20mass%20operation%20to%20silence%20critics%20across%20soci