side%20casino%20resorts%20across%20the%20seaside%20city%3A%20the%20casual%2C%20British-themed%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Pub%20%26amp%3B%20Grill%3B%20the%20slightly%20elevated%20steakhouse%2C%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Steak%3B%20and%20the%20flashy%2C%20TV-inspired%20Hell's%20Kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETogether%2C%20they%20showcase%20what%20celebrity-chef%20dining%20looks%20like%20in%202026%3A%20upscale%20but%20accessible%2C%20familiar%20but%20celebratory%2C%20slightly%20expensive%20without%20being%20exclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%20glance%2C%20Ramsay's%20restaurants%20may%20appear%20worlds%20away%20from%20what%20I've%20come%20to%20expect%20at%20the%20casual-dining%20chains%20that%20I%20frequent%20as%20a%20food%20reporter%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchilis-vs-applebees-which-is-better-review-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EApplebee's%20or%20Chili's%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20interiors%20are%20more%20polished.%20The%20food%20is%20more%20elevated.%20The%20prices%20are%20a%20whole%20lot%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20as%20I%20dined%20my%20way%20through%20Ramsay's%20restaurants%2C%20a%20through%20line%20emerged.%20At%20both%20casual-dining%20chains%20and%20chef-branded%20spots%20like%20Hell's%20Kitchen%2C%20I%20wondered%20how%20much%20I%20was%20really%20paying%20for%20the%20food%2C%20and%20how%20much%20for%20the%20comfort%20of%20knowing%20exactly%20what%20to%20expect%20from%20my%20dining%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeneath%20the%20luxe%20lighting%20and%20famous%20name%2C%20celebrity-chef%20restaurants%20operate%20on%20the%20same%20principle%20that%20keeps%20casual%20chains%20packed%20night%20after%20night%3A%20familiarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226bb9c896-bae4-4536-b44e-f6a3a73bd485%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELike%20casual-dining%20chains%2C%20celebrity-chef%20restaurants%20lean%20into%20comfort%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Pub%20%26amp%3B%20Grill%2C%20the%20most%20casual%20of%20the%20three%20restaurants%20I%20visited%20in%20July%202025%2C%20the%20menu%20served%20fancier%20versions%20of%20classic%20pub%20grub.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gordon%20ramsay%20pub%20and%20grill%20atlantic%20city%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689f71c4a17a8c5b4052f6d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGordon%20Ramsay's%20Pub%20Burger%20came%20with%20fries%20and%20ketchup%20for%20dipping.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20Buffalo%20cauliflower%20fried%20in%20batter%20and%20smothered%20in%20sauce%2C%20mac%20and%20cheese%20made%20with%20rich%20English%20cheddar%2C%20and%20a%20classic%20pub%20burger%20topped%20with%20cheese%2C%20bacon%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20and%20pickles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20balance%20between%20familiarity%20and%20flair%20is%20intentional%2C%20says%20Christopher%20Carraher%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20food%20and%20beverage%20for%20Caesars%20Entertainment%2C%20which%20oversees%20many%20of%20Ramsay's%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20we%20need%20recognizable%20staples%20that%20ground%20the%20menu%20and%20make%20it%20approachable%2C%26quot%3B%20Carraher%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20there%2C%20we%20let%20the%20chef's%20creativity%20shine%20through%20dishes%20that%20are%20bold%20and%20completely%20unique%20to%20the%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22applebees%20cheeseburger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6778184a59d276c1cdaff49d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApplebee's%20burger%20was%20clearly%20less%20fancy%2C%20but%20it's%20still%20a%20good%20burger.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECarraher%20said%20that%20while%20recognizable%20dishes%20anchor%20the%20menu%2C%20innovation%20is%20layered%20on%20top.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20dining%20experience%20that%20feels%20both%20comforting%20and%20exciting%2C%20sometimes%20within%20the%20same%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20experienced%20that%20for%20myself%20at%20Ramsay's%20restaurants.%20The%20pub%20burger%20at%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Pub%20%26amp%3B%20Grill%20was%20juicy%2C%20well-seasoned%2C%20and%20featured%20classic%20ingredients%20you%20would%20find%20on%20most%20bar-and-grill%20burgers%2C%20but%20was%20slightly%20elevated%20with%20a%20red-wine%20glaze%20and%20prime%20sirloin%20patty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20typical%20chain-restaurant%20fare%20kicked%20up%20a%20notch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a960c260-c39d-44fa-b18c-46a463d59b1c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrity-chef%20restaurants%20and%20casual%20chains%20take%20the%20gamble%20out%20of%20leisure%20dining%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gordon%20ramsay%20hells%20kitchen%20atlantic%20city%20new%20jersey%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af61cca17a8c5b40539bf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20host%20stand%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20in%20Atlantic%20City%20also%20sells%20merchandise.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ECelebrity-chef%20restaurants%20are%20often%20found%20inside%20casinos%2C%20and%20they%20make%20the%20most%20sense%20in%20vacation%20locales%20like%20Atlantic%20City%2C%20Vegas%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmiami-next-silicon-valley-weirder-palantir-zuck-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiami%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20places%20where%20tourists%20want%20one%20or%20two%20%26quot%3Bnice%20dinners%26quot%3B%20but%20are%20overwhelmed%20by%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20want%20a%20safe%20option%3A%20reliable%20food%2C%20good%20service%2C%20and%20a%20price%20point%20that's%20slightly%20higher%20than%20what%20they'd%20usually%20spend%2C%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20a%20special%20evening%20without%20breaking%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20cities%20with%20hundreds%20of%20restaurants%2C%20a%20celebrity%20chef's%20name%20cuts%20through%20the%20noise.%20A%202024%20survey%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftalkerresearch.com%2Fwho-is-americas-favorite-celebrity-chef%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETalker%20Research%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20Americans%20would%20be%20willing%20to%20pay%20%24340%20on%20average%20for%20a%20three-course%20meal%20prepared%20by%20their%20favorite%20celebrity%20chef%20%E2%80%94%2040%25%20of%20whom%20said%20Ramsay%20was%20their%20top%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20about%2017%25%20would%20spend%20more%20than%20%24500.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarraher%20added%20that%20the%20details%20in%20celebrity-chef%20restaurants%20%E2%80%94%20from%20lighting%20and%20music%20to%20uniforms%20and%20packaging%20%E2%80%94%20are%20carefully%20designed%20to%20reflect%20the%20chef's%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gordon%20ramsay%20hells%20kitchen%20atlantic%20city%20new%20jersey%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af61cccfc04e97619c2774%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECocktails%20were%20garnished%20with%20pitchfork%20toothpicks%20in%20another%20example%20of%20branding.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDiners%20are%20drawn%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20they're%20experiencing%20something%20personally%20curated%20by%20their%20favorite%20chef%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20sense%20of%20trust%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20a%20well-known%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20part%20of%20the%20appeal%20of%20dining%20at%20a%20celebrity-chef%20chain%20is%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-gordon-ramsay-beef-wellington-first-time-worth-it-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeef%20Wellington%3C%2Fa%3E%20you%20order%20at%20Ramsay's%20Atlantic%20City%20restaurants%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20one%20you%20order%20in%20London%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20or%20Miami.%20And%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20know%20what%20will%20be%20on%20the%20menu%20by%20the%20time%20you%20arrive%20for%20your%20reservation%2C%20you%20already%20know%20Ramsay's%20name%20and%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20diners%2C%20that's%20enough%20to%20make%20them%20feel%20comfortable%20trusting%20a%20place%20like%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20for%20their%20only%20meal%20out%20on%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20celebrity%20chefs%20and%20restaurateurs%20also%20follow%20this%20model.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-bobby-flay-burger-restaurant-bobbys-burgers-photos-meal-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBobby%20Flay's%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20portfolio%20reliably%20showcases%20his%20Southwestern%20style%20%E2%80%94%20think%20bold%20spices%20and%20chili%20peppers%20%E2%80%94%20with%20his%20signature%20burgers%20and%20meat-focused%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGuy%20Fieri's%20outposts%20lean%20into%20the%20same%20over-the-top%20comfort%20food%20and%20flame-heavy%20branding%20that%20define%20his%20TV%20persona.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vanderpump%20cocktail%20garden%20vegas%20goat%20cheese%20balls%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0be381fb3fcb426488b4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESUR's%20signature%20goat-cheese%20balls%20have%20become%20a%20staple%20across%20Lisa%20Vanderpump's%20restaurant%20empire.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELisa%20Vanderpump's%20venues%20similarly%20pair%20ornate%2C%20maximalist%20d%C3%A9cor%20with%20photo-ready%20cocktails%20and%20indulgent%20small%20plates%2C%20including%20SUR's%20signature%20goat-cheese%20balls%2C%20a%20dish%20made%20famous%20on%20her%20reality%20show%20%26quot%3BVanderpump%20Rules.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20each%20celebrity's%20restaurant%20portfolio%2C%20the%20through%20line%20is%20familiarity%3A%20recognizable%20dishes%2C%20consistent%20aesthetics%2C%20and%20a%20clear%20extension%20of%20the%20celebrity's%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20logic%20fuels%20chain%20restaurants%20like%20Applebee's%20and%20Chili's.%20Their%20casual%2C%20comfortable%20interiors%20and%20photo-heavy%20menus%20are%20designed%20to%20feel%20familiar%20and%20predictable%2C%20helping%20ensure%20diners%20know%20exactly%20what%20they're%20ordering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDiners%20actively%20seek%20out%20that%20kind%20of%20reassurance.%20A%202023%20survey%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usfoods.com%2Ftools-tips-and-ideas%2Farticles-and-publications%2Farticles%2Famerican-menu-choices%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%2083%25%20of%20diners%20review%20a%20restaurant's%20menu%20before%20arriving%2C%20and%20half%20(50%25)%20make%20their%20final%20decision%20on%20what%20they'll%20order%20before%20even%20sitting%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22503d4023-2c7e-43a3-97eb-cd72dbfe251b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrity-chef%20restaurants%20have%20a%20leg%20up%20on%20casual%20chains%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20atmosphere%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gordon%20ramsay%20hells%20kitchen%20atlantic%20city%20new%20jersey%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68af61daa17a8c5b40539bf8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20energy%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20was%20exciting%2C%20and%20the%20decor%20was%20sleek%20and%20elevated.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHell's%20Kitchen%20crackled%20with%20energy%2C%20its%20open%20kitchen%20alive%20with%20sizzling%20pans%20and%20servers%20hustling%20dishes%20out%20to%20awaiting%20tables.%20Photos%20of%20past%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freview-is-hells-kitchen-restaurant-worth-it-for-couple-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHell's%20Kitchen%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20winners%20lined%20the%20walls%20while%20screens%20throughout%20the%20dining%20room%20played%20clips%20from%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EServers%20also%20encouraged%20photos%20as%20dishes%20emerged%20from%20the%20open%20chef's%20kitchen%2C%20making%20it%20feel%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Emore%20like%20a%20performance%20than%20just%20a%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20simply%20don't%20get%20that%20at%20Applebee's%2C%20and%20that's%20one%20reason%20people%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20a%20Ramsay-branded%20establishment%20over%20a%20casual-dining%20chain%20when%20visiting%20a%20vacation%20destination%20like%20Atlantic%20City%2C%20where%20both%20types%20of%20restaurants%20are%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20sense%20of%20luxury%20is%20more%20theatrical%20than%20literal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20that%20reservations%20at%20all%20three%20of%20Ramsay's%20restaurants%20were%20relatively%20easy%20to%20get%2C%20even%20during%20the%20height%20of%20summer.%20Like%20most%20large-scale%20restaurant%20groups%2C%20the%20kitchens%20are%20run%20by%20trained%20executive%20chefs%20and%20culinary%20teams%20rather%20than%20by%20Ramsay%20himself.%20The%20experience%20is%20designed%20to%20feel%20celebratory%20and%20polished%2C%20but%20still%20accessible%20%E2%80%94%20special%20without%20being%20overly%20formal%20or%20intimidating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20it's%20still%20a%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2233f9bb17-5054-43d5-911d-27f3d46951c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECelebrity-chef%20restaurants%20aren't%20scams%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20so%20different%20from%20other%20chain%20restaurants%2C%20either%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ken%20Todd%2C%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20and%20Lisa%20Vanderpump%20celebrate%20the%20grand%20opening%20of%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Burger%20at%20Flamingo%20Las%20Vegas%20on%20January%2016%2C%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69442d3204eda4732f2dc923%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKen%20Todd%2C%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20and%20Lisa%20Vanderpump%20celebrate%20the%20grand%20opening%20of%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Burger%20at%20Flamingo%20Las%20Vegas%20on%20January%2016%2C%202025.%3Cp%3EDenise%20Truscello%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Caesars%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGordon%20Ramsay%20Restaurants%20operates%2094%20restaurants%20worldwide%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Flelalondon%2F2025%2F03%2F04%2Fgordon-ramsay-on-the-business-of-building-an-empire%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20and%20generated%20revenues%20of%20%24500.8%20million%20in%202024.%20His%20restaurant%20group%20also%20holds%20an%20impressive%20eight%20Michelin%20stars%2C%20including%20three%20at%20his%20flagship%2C%20Restaurant%20Gordon%20Ramsay%2C%20which%20he%20has%20maintained%20for%20more%20than%2022%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinancially%2C%20those%20numbers%20pale%20in%20comparison%20to%20massive%20chains%20like%20Applebee's%2C%20which%20brought%20in%20%244.1%20billion%20in%20sales%20in%202024%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restaurantbusinessonline.com%2Ftop-500-chains-2025%2Fapplebees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERestaurant%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20and%20has%201%2C614%20locations%20worldwide%20%E2%80%94%20but%2C%20perhaps%20no%20surprise%20here%2C%20zero%20Michelin%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20both%20types%20of%20chain-restaurant%20concepts%2C%20there's%20a%20focus%20on%20expansion%20and%20attracting%20both%20new%20and%20returning%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20one%20challenge%20that%20celebrity-chef%20restaurants%20face%20is%20price%20creep.%20The%20cost%20of%20an%20average%20meal%20can%20quickly%20outpace%20what%20value-focused%20chain-restaurant%20diners%20are%20used%20to%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Pub%20%26amp%3B%20Grill%2C%20dinner%20for%20two%20%E2%80%94%20entr%C3%A9es%2C%20appetizers%2C%20cocktails%2C%20and%20a%20side%20%E2%80%94%20totaled%20%24181.42%20after%20tax%20and%20tip.%20The%20nearly%20%2430%20pub%20burger%20was%20well%20executed%2C%20but%20comparable%20to%20versions%20I've%20had%20elsewhere%20for%20far%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jump%20was%20even%20more%20pronounced%20at%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20Steak%2C%20where%20dinner%20for%20two%20%E2%80%94%20including%20four%20cocktails%20and%20no%20sides%20%E2%80%94%20totaled%20%24320%20after%20tax%20and%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223072%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22gordon%20ramsay%20steak%20atlantic%20city%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b0804ca17a8c5b4053aa0e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222304%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20steak%20was%20super%20tender%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20little%20overpriced.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20%24100-plus%20American%20wagyu%20filet%20was%20tender%20and%20well%20seasoned%2C%20but%20lacked%20the%20marbling%20or%20wow%20factor%20to%20justify%20its%20premium%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20at%20Hell's%20Kitchen%20%E2%80%94%20the%20strongest%20of%20the%20three%20experiences%20%E2%80%94%20value%20hinged%20more%20on%20atmosphere%20than%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20meal%20for%20two%20cost%20%24210.22.%20I%20thought%20this%20was%20reasonable%20for%20a%20celebratory%20night%20out%2C%20but%20far%20beyond%20what%20I'd%20spend%20at%20a%20casual%20chain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou're%20not%20paying%20for%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20to%20cook%20your%20steak.%20You're%20paying%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidea%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20cooking%20your%20steak%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20way%20you're%20paying%20for%20the%20comfort%20of%20Applebee's%20consistency%20when%20you%20pull%20off%20the%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20just%20comes%20with%20a%20pitchfork%20toothpick%20inside%20a%20%2420%20cocktail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGordon%20Ramsay%20Restaurant%20Group%20did%20not%20return%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-restaurants-applebees-chain-restaurants-compared-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772449381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F698cb135a645d118818922d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-restaurants-applebees-chain-restaurants-compared-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Behind%20the%20sleek%20branding%20and%20star%20power%2C%20do%20celebrity-chef%20restaurants%20actually%20stand%20apart%20from%20your%20local%20neighborhood%20grill%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22emcdowell%40businessinsider.com%20(Erin%20McDowell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcelebrity-chef-restaurants-applebees-chain-restaurants-compared-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US-Iran%20war%3A%20'Several'%20American%20warplanes%20crash%20in%20Kuwait%2C%20crew%20survive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772449380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-128944940%2Cimgsize-78782.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-iran-war-several-american-warplanes-crash-in-kuwait-crew-survive%2