ps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-israel-war-top-intelligence-officials-killed-in-saturdays-strikes-on-iran-israel-11158247%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20led%20communications%20at%20FEMA%20during%20a%20hurricane%2C%20and%20had%20to%20flee%20my%20home%20after%20a%20death%20threat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222341%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jaclyn%20Rothenberg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a35bf7d3e2f1aef369c02c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJaclyn%20Rothenberg%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Avoq%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJaclyn%20Rothenberg%2C%20a%20former%20FEMA%20spokesperson%2C%20faced%20online%20threats%20during%20her%20time%20at%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAt%20one%20point%2C%20Rothenberg%20had%20to%20leave%20her%20home%20because%20of%20safety%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20now%20counsels%20companies%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecurity-threats-have-some-boards-rethinking-exec-security-2026-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erisks%20leaders%20and%20others%20face%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20how%20they%20can%20prepare.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Jaclyn%20Rothenberg%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20for%20reputation%20management%20at%20Avoq%2C%20a%20communications%20and%20lobbying%20firm.%20From%20July%202021%20to%20late%202024%2C%20she%20was%20a%20spokesperson%20and%20director%20of%20public%20affairs%20at%20the%20Federal%20Emergency%20Management%20Agency.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20brevity%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20fall%20of%202024.%20I%20was%20the%20director%20of%20public%20affairs%20at%20FEMA%20during%20Hurricanes%20Helene%20and%20Milton%2C%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20moment%20in%20the%20world%20of%20misinformation%20because%20there%20was%20so%20much%20of%20it%2C%20so%20fast.%20And%20it%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20election%20cycle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20was%20to%20communicate%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20administration.%20The%20primary%20goal%20was%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20were%20connected%20to%20services%20and%20support%20so%20they%20could%20get%20back%20on%20their%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20response%2C%20as%20we%20were%20communicating%20safety%20and%20recovery%20information%2C%20other%20public%20officials%20and%20I%20were%20targeted.%20A%20mix%20of%20people%20were%20insinuating%20that%20we%20weren't%20doing%20our%20job.%20They%20were%20also%20spreading%20misinformation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20reflect%2C%20what%20was%20really%20surprising%20to%20me%20at%20the%20time%20was%20getting%20attacked%20for%20my%20religion.%20I'm%20Jewish.%20There%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20online%20who%20could%20say%20anything%20and%20everything%20without%20knowing%20me%20%E2%80%94%20very%20hurtful%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d27fe42-47ca-4adf-9afc-9d1765347959%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'How%20can%20you%20keep%20doing%20this%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20my%20husband%20saying%20how%20upset%20he%20was.%20I%20think%20I%20had%20mentally%20tried%20to%20block%20out%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%20because%20I%20felt%20empowered%20by%20continuing%20to%20do%20my%20job%20and%20communicating%20life-saving%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20remember%20him%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20you%20keep%20doing%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20reality%20is%2C%20I%20was%20hired%20to%20do%20a%20job.%20In%20Judaism%2C%20they%20really%20do%20teach%20you%20to%20do%20what's%20best%20for%20people.%20It's%20a%20phrase%20called%20%3Cem%3Etikkun%20olam.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20continued%20to%20work%20through%20it%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could.%20The%20social%20media%20posts%20made%20fun%20of%20my%20appearance%2C%20my%20last%20name.%20There%20were%20very%20terrible%20things%20said%20and%20photos%20that%20were%20shared%2C%20and%20very%20antisemitic%20rhetoric.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20forced%20the%20agency%20to%20put%20security%20protection%20on%20me%2C%20because%20someone%20threatened%20to%20kill%20me.%20That%20was%20surreal%20because%20I%20was%20hired%20to%20be%20a%20communications%20lead%20for%20the%20agency.%20I%20was%20technically%20a%20political%20appointee%2C%20as%20a%20Biden%20administration%20official.%20Still%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20one%20of%20the%20first%20times%20when%20people%20weren't%20just%20going%20after%20politicians%2C%20but%20also%20federal%20employees%20for%20doing%20what%20they%20were%20hired%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20contractor%20had%20been%20working%20with%20us%20to%20help%20identify%20misinformation.%20I%20believe%20they%20alerted%20the%20senior-most%20folks%20at%20my%20agency%2C%20who%20then%20brought%20the%20threat%20to%20my%20attention.%20Everyone%20was%20working%20almost%2024-hour%20days.%20A%20colleague%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20speak%20with%20you%20urgently.%26quot%3B%20They%20told%20me%20that%20there%20was%20a%20real%2C%20serious%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22068fc54d-ae70-4806-9096-dc540455c953%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStaying%20vigilant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20catalyst%20was%20a%20public%20statement%20I%20had%20put%20out%2C%20pushing%20back%20against%20misinformation.%20I%20left%20my%20home%20because%20the%20people%20who%20were%20targeting%20me%20online%20found%20my%20address%2C%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20my%20parents.%20They%20looked%20into%20my%20work%20history.%20I%20called%20my%20husband%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20to%20call%20our%20friends.%20We%20need%20to%20sleep%20there.%20Let's%20get%20the%20dogs%20and%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20senior%20leadership%20personally%20reached%20out%20to%20ensure%20that%20I%20felt%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20just%20my%20parents%20and%20my%20husband.%20They%20identified%20my%20extended%20relatives%20and%20posted%20those%20on%20social%20media.%20The%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eagency%20worked%20hard%20to%20help%20me%20scrub%20some%20of%20that%2C%20and%20I'm%20thankful%20for%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20something%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20companies%20should%20be%20thinking%20about.%20It's%20important%20for%20people%20to%20stay%20vigilant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221e3a5633-7191-4f58-ae74-388465482459%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20not%20just%20the%20CEO%20they're%20going%20after%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20hindsight%2C%20the%20incident%20was%20probably%20more%20traumatizing%20than%20it%20felt%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20because%20I%20think%20I%20was%20in%20shock.%20Also%2C%20I%20was%20still%20doing%20my%20job.%20I%20was%20committed%20to%20communicating%20in%20these%20critical%20moments%20for%20survivors%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20fully%20hit%20me%20%E2%80%94%20the%20magnitude%20of%20that%20incident%20%E2%80%94%20until%20months%20later.%20The%20fact%20that%20I%20had%20to%20be%20silenced%20for%20my%20own%20protection%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20couldn't%20help%20other%20people%20was%20hard%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20tone%20down%20public%20communication%20from%20the%20spokesperson%20account.%20I%20had%20to%20stop%20doing%20media%20interviews%20about%20the%20topics%20that%20I%20was%20trying%20to%20get%20out%20there.%20We%20saw%20a%20decrease%20in%20registration%20for%20assistance.%20There%20was%20real%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20one%20of%20the%20things%20I've%20counseled%20clients%20on%2C%20both%20at%20the%20C-suite%20level%20and%20below%2C%20is%20that%20it's%20not%20just%20the%20CEO%20they're%20going%20after.%20They'll%20go%20after%20the%20head%20of%20HR%2C%20the%20head%20of%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20new%20normal%2C%20unfortunately.%20It's%20important%20for%20companies%20to%20do%20exercises%20on%20how%20to%20respond%20and%20how%20they%20can%20protect%20their%20senior%20executives%20and%20employees%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20have%20to%20think%20about%20what%20protection%20looks%20like%20from%20a%20privacy%20standpoint%20on%20social%20media.%20I%20don't%20think%20people%20really%20realize%20the%20online%20footprint%20that%20they%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20a%20challenging%20experience%20in%20your%20career%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-fema-spokesperson-faced-online-threats-from-misinformation-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772448061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a35bf7d3e2f1aef369c02c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-fema-spokesperson-faced-online-threats-from-misinformation-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jaclyn%20Rothenberg%20faced%20doxxing%20and%20threats%20while%20working%20as%20a%20FEMA%20spokesperson%20during%20Hurricanes%20Helene%20and%20Milton.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fformer-fema-spokesperson-faced-online-threats-from-misinformation-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Canada%20sign%20uranium%20deal%2C%20vow%20to%20finalise%20economic%20partnership%20soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772448058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg