Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20typical%20day%2C%20Delmonico's%20will%20serve%20about%20150%20for%20lunch%20and%20300%20for%20dinner%2C%20Dennis%20Turcinovic%2C%20the%20owner%2C%20told%20me.%20The%20restaurant%20hosts%20around%2025%20weekly%20corporate%20events%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20private%20dinner%20menus%20for%20a%20defense%20tech%20giant%2C%20a%20law%20firm%2C%20and%20tech%20companies%20hanging%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Their%20signature%20is%20the%2018-ounce%20Delmonico%20ribeye%2C%20for%20%2489%2C%20and%20a%20waiter%20told%20me%20the%20%2446%20mushroom%20risotto%20is%20an%20underappreciated%20menu%20standout.%20Employees%20are%20also%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20the%20restaurant%20invented%20baked%20Alaska%2C%20a%20dessert%20that%20goes%20for%20%2425.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReservations%20open%20six%20months%20in%20advance%20to%20accommodate%20tourists%20planning%20trips%20to%20New%20York%2C%20but%20the%20chef%20told%20me%20that%20some%20business%20regulars%20have%20employees'%20personal%20numbers%20and%20can%20always%20get%20in.%20Turcinovic%20estimated%20that%20around%2025%25%20of%20diners%20are%20monthly%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalking%20around%20a%20deserted%2C%20ginormous%20restaurant%20felt%20semi-apocalyptic%20against%20the%20din%20of%20seemingly%20endless%20prep%20%E2%80%94%20the%20vacuuming%20lasted%20more%20than%20an%20hour%2C%20employees%20hauled%20potted%20plants%20across%20the%20dining%20room%2C%20line%20cooks%20talked%20over%20the%20white%20noise%20of%20knives%20on%20cutting%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Delmonico's%20interior%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a08c8e1fb3fcb42648845d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20restaurant%20was%20eerily%20empty%20but%20set.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20churn%20of%20prep%2C%20Turcinovic%20said%20the%20business%20lunch%20at%20Delmonico's%20isn't%20what%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%20partly%20because%20of%20how%20the%20pandemic%20changed%20our%20office%20schedules.%20But%20there's%20something%20else%20going%20on%2C%20too%3A%20companies%20are%20building%20their%20own%20swanky%20cafeterias%20or%20restaurants.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-splurging-on-free-lunch-perks-catering-microsoft-meta-google-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFree%2C%20fancy%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20perks%20employers%20are%20still%20investing%20in%2C%20as%20Wall%20Street%20in%20particular%20demands%20workers%20spend%20more%20time%20in%20the%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFood%20makes%20the%20office%20more%20palatable%2C%20especially%20for%20younger%20employees%20who%20place%20a%20premium%20on%20boutique%20benefits.%20Turcinovic%20and%20a%20few%20other%20senior%20employees%20at%20Delmonico's%20mentioned%20JPMorgan's%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-new-headquarters-building-message-work-as-life-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%243%20billion%20headquarters%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20me%2C%20which%20boasts%20a%20pub%2C%20coffee%20bars%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-headquarters-270-park-food-dining-coffee-vegan-morgans-pub-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efood%20hall%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20Little%20Dirt%20Candy%2C%20a%20scaled-down%20version%20of%20a%20Michelin-starred%20vegan%20restaurant.%20Turcinovic%20said%20he%20has%20a%20friend%20who%20works%20at%20the%20bank%20and%20dines%20in%20the%20building%2C%20both%20alone%20and%20with%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20bring%20them%20into%20the%20building.%20They%20do%20entertain%20them%20there%20because%20business%20can%20get%20done%20anywhere%20where%20there's%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20sure%20to%20add%20that%20there's%20something%20inherently%20different%20about%20going%20to%20a%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223515%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shrimp%20at%20Delmonico's%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a08dd750f42603b0f8f830%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222636%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDespite%20my%20best%20efforts%2C%20I%20was%20consistently%20in%20the%20way%20when%20walking%20around%20the%20prep%20kitchen.%3Cp%3EAlice%20Tecotzky%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20isn't%20alone%20in%20trying%20to%20turn%20the%20office%20into%20a%20dining%20hot%20spot%3A%20KKR%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20all%20seem%20to%20have%20a%20similar%20idea%2C%20to%20name%20just%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20no%20one%20on%20Wall%20Street%20goes%20out%20to%20lunch%20anymore.%20Even%20after%20some%20firms%20relocated%20from%20downtown%20to%20Midtown%20following%209%2F11%20%E2%80%94%20a%20shift%20Turcinovic%20said%20the%20restaurant%20%26quot%3Bfelt%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Delmonico's%20still%20caters%20to%20high-finance%20tastes.%20Just%20look%20at%20the%20buckets%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsaratoga-spring-water-everywhere-milken-global-conference-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaratoga%20water%20bottles%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethroughout%20the%20dining%20room%2C%20the%20same%20ones%20I%20saw%20in%20excess%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftommy-bahama-midtown-manhattan-finance-wall-street-power-lunch-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETommy%20Bahama%2C%20surprisingly%20popular%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20the%20Midtown-based%20finance%20crowd%2C%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saratoga%20water%20bottles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a09407e8408f66718054a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfi