ased%20in%20Singapore%20and%20has%20been%20at%20McKinsey%20for%20just%20over%20eight-and-a-half%20years.%20As%20a%20leader%20of%20QuantumBlack%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-ai-mckinsey-bcg-deloitte-pwc-kpmg-chatbots-ai-tools-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Efirm's%20AI%20arm%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20he%20helps%20lead%20the%20firm's%20data%20science%20and%20technical%20teams%20across%20Southeast%20Asia.%20He%20holds%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20computer%20science%20and%20mathematics%20from%20Imperial%20College%20London.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20distinguish%20yourself%20to%20get%20promoted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20focused%20on%20doing%20a%20few%20things%20consistently%20well%20rather%20than%20trying%20to%20do%20everything.%20I%20leaned%20into%20my%20strengths%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20at%20the%20intersection%20of%20analytics%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20human%20judgment%20%E2%80%94%20to%20make%20my%20contributions%20clearly%20valuable%20to%20clients.%20I%20also%20invested%20deeply%20in%20people%2C%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20understand%20what%20motivated%20team%20members%2C%20support%20their%20careers%2C%20and%20create%20environments%20where%20they%20could%20do%20their%20best%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20changed%20in%20your%20behavior%20or%20performance%20as%20you%20climbed%20the%20ranks%20to%20make%20partner%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20shift%20was%20moving%20from%20being%20good%20at%20my%20own%20work%20to%20making%20first%20a%20few%2C%20then%20many%2C%20other%20people%20successful.%20As%20I%20progressed%2C%20I%20became%20more%20intentional%20about%20building%20teams%20and%20creating%20impact%20for%20clients%20beyond%20any%20single%20project.%20In%20practice%2C%20that%20meant%20spending%20more%20time%20coaching%20than%20doing%20the%20work%20myself%2C%20and%20being%20explicit%20about%20sharing%20context%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20so%20I%20could%20step%20back%20and%20let%20others%20step%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20metrics%20or%20signals%20told%20you%20that%20you%20were%20on%20track%20for%20partner%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20clear%20signal%20was%20when%20feedback%20shifted%20from%20what%20I%20was%20delivering%20to%20the%20impact%20I%20was%20having%20on%20the%20system.%20Senior%20colleagues%20began%20commenting%20on%20the%20teams%20I%20was%20building%20and%20the%20leaders%20I%20was%20developing.%20One%20piece%20of%20feedback%20that%20stuck%20with%20me%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BYou're%20starting%20to%20leave%20things%20better%20than%20you%20found%20them%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%20you've%20moved%20on.%26quot%3B%20It%20reframed%20success%3A%20not%20being%20indispensable%20on%20a%20project%2C%20but%20being%20replaceable%20because%20I'd%20built%20something%20self-sustaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20non-negotiable%20indulgence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20Singapore%2C%20I'm%20fortunate%20to%20have%20a%20view%20of%20Marina%20Bay.%20My%20one%20non-negotiable%20with%20work%20travel%20is%20being%20home%20for%20major%20celebrations%20so%20I%20can%20spend%20time%20with%20my%20partner%20and%20catch%20the%20fireworks.%20We%20just%20celebrated%20Lunar%20New%20Year%20%E2%80%94%20lots%20of%20good%20food%20and%20an%20impressive%20amount%20of%20fireworks%20lighting%20up%20the%20bay.%20It's%20one%20of%20those%20moments%20that%20makes%20it%20worth%20planning%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275cdbddd-7237-4875-9e0d-3af708ab1078%5C%22%3EJen%20Malandra%2C%2037%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jen%20Malandra%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a21bf1fd4fbd083f2940df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJen%20Malandra%3Cp%3EMcKinsey%20%26amp%3B%20Company%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBoston-based%20Malandra%2C%20who%20will%20mark%20eight%20years%20at%20the%20firm%20this%20summer%2C%20previously%20served%20eight%20years%20in%20the%20Navy%20before%20transitioning%20to%20consulting.%20She%20now%20focuses%20on%20operational%20transformation%2C%20helping%20clients%20scale%20production%20and%20redesign%20manufacturing%20systems.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20were%20your%20most%20important%20senior%20sponsors%2C%20and%20how%20did%20you%20build%20those%20relationships%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20experience%2C%20sponsors%20don't%20come%20from%20networking%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20they%20form%20when%20someone%20sees%20your%20authentic%20passion%20in%20action%20and%20wants%20to%20build%20alongside%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20a%20manufacturing%20client%20aiming%20to%20grow%20organically%20by%20producing%20more%20with%20the%20same%20lines%20and%20workforce.%20I%20became%20deeply%20invested%20in%20training%20the%20entire%20workforce%20%E2%80%94%20from%20frontline%20operators%20to%20plant%20leadership%20%E2%80%94%20to%20identify%20opportunities%20for%20improvement%20and%20lead%20a%20transformation%20owned%20from%20the%20floor%20up%2C%20not%20imposed%20from%20above.%20I%20threw%20myself%20into%20designing%20and%20delivering%20those%20trainings%20and%20loved%20being%20on%20the%20floor%20helping%20workers%20see%20their%20impact%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20leader%20noticed%20that%20energy%20and%20asked%20me%20to%20partner%20with%20him%20on%20similar%20client%20work%20and%20later%20on%20internal%20initiatives.%20His%20support%20lasted%20for%20years%2C%20and%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20people%20I%20called%20when%20I%20was%20elected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I've%20progressed%2C%20I've%20tried%20to%20model%20that%20same%20approach%20with%20those%20I%20sponsor.%20I%20believe%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20want%20to%20be%20on%20my%20team%20matters%20just%20as%20much%20as%20the%20number%20of%20leaders%20who%20want%20me%20on%20theirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20changed%20in%20your%20behavior%20or%20performance%20as%20you%20climbed%20the%20ranks%20to%20make%20partner%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20lessons%20I've%20applied%20throughout%20my%20career%20is%20the%2080-20%20principle%2C%20which%20McKinsey%20teaches%20incoming%20consultants%3A%20focus%20on%20the%2020%25%20of%20efforts%20that%20drive%2080%25%20of%20the%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20progressed%20%E2%80%94%20and%20became%20a%20parent%20%E2%80%94%20I%20used%20it%20not%20just%20to%20deliver%20results%20for%20clients%2C%20but%20to%20prioritize%20my%20time%20and%20energy%20more%20broadly.%20It%20helped%20me%20focus%20on%20what%20mattered%20most%2C%20professionally%20and%20personally%2C%20and%20be%20more%20intentional%20about%20empowering%20others%20and%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20they%20could%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20metrics%20or%20signals%20told%20you%20that%20you%20were%20on%20track%20for%20partner%20versus%20just%20being%20a%20high%20performer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20fortunate%20to%20work%20with%20senior%20leaders%20who%20invested%20in%20my%20development.%20A%20clear%20signal%20I%20was%20on%20the%20right%20track%20was%20the%20growing%20trust%20they%20placed%20in%20me.%20I%20remember%20when%20a%20senior%20partner%20invited%20me%20to%20join%20a%20client%20offsite%20to%20discuss%20strategy%20changes%3B%20what%20began%20as%20a%20chance%20to%20contribute%20quickly%20became%20an%20opportunity%20to%20lead%20the%20work.%20That%20moment%20was%20pivotal%20%E2%80%94%20it%20showed%20me%20they%20saw%20me%20as%20someone%20ready%20to%20take%20on%20more%20responsibility%20and%20deliver%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20your%20non-negotiable%20indulgence%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriday%20night%20pizza%20with%20my%20family.%20After%20a%20busy%20workweek%2C%20there's%20nothing%20be