%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a0acdafd4fbd083f2922c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Lawrence%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Morgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20companies%20move%20to%20lay%20off%20workers%20and%20shift%20to%20AI%2C%20panic%20is%20creeping%20in%20across%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20Andrew%20Slimmon%20of%20Morgan%20Stanley%20Investment%20Management%20isn't%20worried%20about%20AI%20disruption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20his%20view%2C%20the%20rise%20of%20AI%20will%20create%20new%20jobs%2C%20just%20as%20the%20dot-com%20revolution%20did.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20worried%20about%20losing%20your%20job%20to%20AI%20in%202026%2C%20you're%20not%20alone%2C%20but%20one%20Wall%20Street%20exec%20thinks%20the%20panic%20isn't%20warranted.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Slimmon%2C%20head%20of%20applied%20equity%20advisors%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%20Investment%20Management%2C%20isn't%20too%20concerned%20about%20the%20AI%20scare%20trade%20or%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20AI%20is%20impacting%20white-collar%20workers%20in%20the%20US.%20While%20he%20doesn't%20doubt%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20disruptive%2C%20he%20doesn't%20buy%20one%20of%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emost%20popular%20narratives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20topic%20of%20AI-driven%20job%20loss%20came%20sharply%20into%20focus%20this%20week%20when%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-boom-recession-citrini-research-layoffs-jobs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eviral%20Substack%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20market%20research%20firm%20Citrini%20Research%20predicted%20a%20white-collar%20jobs%20wipeout%20in%20a%20few%20years'%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Slimmon%20sees%20it%2C%20this%20is%20simply%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20cycle%20in%20which%20new%20jobs%20will%20be%20created%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20dawn%20of%20the%20internet%20era%20in%20the%20early%202000s.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20still%20work%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20we're%20just%20more%20productive.%20And%20I%20think%20that'll%20be%20the%20story%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlimmon%20recalls%20similar%20dire%20predictions%20during%20the%20dot-com%20era%2C%20though%20he%20argues%20that%20commentators%20largely%20missed%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20the%20economy%20would%20evolve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertain%20functions%20moved%20online%2C%20and%20that's%20what%20we%20knew%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20companies%20got%20hurt%2C%20but%20what%20we%20didn't%20know%20initially%2C%20but%20eventually%20happened%2C%20was%20that%20there%20were%20new%20jobs%20that%20would%20come%20along.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESlimmon%20highlighted%20companies%20like%20book%20publishers%20and%20travel%20agencies%20that%20were%20among%20the%20first%20casualties%20of%20the%20dot-com%20revolution.%20Yet%2C%20in%20the%20following%20decades%2C%20these%20industries%20still%20exist.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20he%20remains%20skeptical%20of%20doomsday%20scenarios%20predicting%20a%20world%20without%20software%20engineers%20and%20other%20white%20collar%20functions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20many%20Big%20Tech%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Famzn-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fxyz-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlock%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fcrm-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESalesforce%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20move%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCompanies%2520such%2520as%2520eBay%252C%2520Amazon%2Cmedia%252C%2520finance%252C%2520and%2520retail.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elay%20off%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20AI%20efficiency%20gains%2C%20Slimmon%20said%20he's%20convinced%20that%20panic%20isn't%20warranted%2C%20and%20the%20technology%20will%20change%20the%20nature%20of%20work%20rather%20than%20replace%20human%20labor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-scare-trade-overreaction-nvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-software-nvda-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%20after%20his%20company's%20latest%20earnings%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20thinks%20agentic%20AI%20will%20lead%20to%20engineers%20having%20different%20work%20to%20do%20in%20the%20future%2C%20but%20their%20jobs%20will%20not%20be%20eliminated.%20This%20perspective%20is%20similar%20to%20Slimmon's%20view%20on%20the%20impact%20of%20AI%20on%20the%20broader%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20just%20think%20right%20now%2C%20we're%20just%20focused%20on%20the%20jobs%20that%20are%20going%20to%20be%20lost%2C%20not%20the%20jobs%20that%20are%20going%20to%20be%20created.%20And%20that's%20kind%20of%20that's%20consistent%20with%20early%20cycle%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-dot-com-bubble-internet-economy-morgan-stanley-2026-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772447401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a1a408fd4fbd083f292ee1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-job-losses-dot-com-bubble-internet-economy-morgan-stanley-2026-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Morgan%20Stanley's%20Andrew%20Slimmon%20argues%20AI%20won't%20devastate%20jobs%2C%20predicting%20a%20cycle%20of%20job%20creation%20akin%20to%20the%20early%202000s%20tech%20revolution.%22%2C%22