0on%20strengthening%20my%20base.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20journey%20was%20far%20from%20smooth.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F495179%2Fsubhankar-bala-ias-cleared-upsc-cse-without-coaching-delhi-shares-strategy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWithout%20coaching%20or%20mentors%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rupam%20often%20doubted%20herself.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20times%20I%20thought%2C%20am%20I%20even%20studying%20the%20right%20way%3F%20Am%20I%20wasting%20my%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20constant%20self-doubt.%20But%20every%20time%20I%20felt%20like%20giving%20up%2C%20my%20mother%E2%80%99s%20face%20on%20her%20deathbed%20came%20before%20me.%20That%20image%20would%20pull%20me%20back.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-2-1757075451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Rupali%2C%20Rupam's%20success%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20clearing%20an%20exam%3B%20it%20was%20proof%20that%20she%20carried%20their%20mother's%20lessons%20through.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-2-1757075451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-2-1757075451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FShe-Lost-Both-Parents-as-a-Teen-But-22-YO-Rupam-Kept-Her-Promise-Cleared-JPSC-in-1st-Attempt-2-1757075451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia