itioned%20his%20premium%20cashew%20sprout%20products%20in%20a%20niche%20market%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20regular%20customers%20Thomas%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20corporate%20chef%20at%20Paragon%20group%20of%20restaurants%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20experienced%20these%20cashew%20sprouts%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20lots%20of%20various%20dishes%20can%20be%20prepared%20with%20adaptability.%20It%20is%20not%20easily%20available%20in%20stores%20so%20people%20have%20some%20curiosity%20about%20it.%20These%20dishes%20are%20repeatedly%20demanded%20from%20our%20happy%20customers%20at%20the%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20positioning%20in%20the%20market%20enabled%20Brijith%20to%20secure%20a%20steady%20clientele%20and%20achieve%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20his%20endeavours%20were%20not%20only%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20innovation%20but%20also%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers.%20By%20purchasing%20wet%20cashews%20from%20at%20least%2011%20local%20farmers%2C%20Brijith%20managed%20to%20provide%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20by%20transforming%20them%20into%20high-quality%20sprouted%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20reimagining%20traditional%20practices%20and%20leveraging%20modern%20technology%2C%20I%20not%20only%20wanted%20to%20revitalise%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20but%20also%20exemplify%20the%20potential%20for%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20in%20rural%20communities.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20wet%20produce%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Brijith%20Krishnan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener