d%20stories%2C%20sang%20songs%2C%20or%20played%20games%20with%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20began%20using%20folk%20tales%2C%20riddles%2C%20and%20interactive%20activities%20to%20make%20learning%20enjoyable.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20children%20started%20participating%20eagerly.%20They%20even%20role-played%20as%20teachers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20police%20officers.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20classroom%20filled%20with%20laughter%20and%20energy.%20When%20the%20children%20laugh%20and%20play%2C%20they%20learn%20without%20even%20realising%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Sangeeta%2C%20these%20moments%20are%20priceless.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20a%20child%20tells%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20teacher%20like%20you%2C%E2%80%99%20my%20heart%20swells%20with%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBalancing%20two%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20school%2C%20Sangeeta%20is%20a%20mother%20and%20wife.%20Married%20in%20Azamgarh%2C%20with%20her%20parental%20home%20in%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20balances%20household%20responsibilities%20with%20teaching.%20Her%20son%2C%20now%20seven%2C%20once%20had%20clashing%20school%20timings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fteachers-day-2-1757060749-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESangeeta%20fulfills%20multiple%20roles%20from%20mentor%20to%20friend%2C%20crucially%20adapting%20her%20skills%20to%20meet%20the%20varied%20needs%20of%20her%20students.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20never%20let%20my%20struggles%20show%20in%20front%20of%20my%20students.%20They%20deserve%20my%20full%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20a%20teacher%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESangeeta%E2%80%99s%20role%20extends%20beyond%20academics.%20She%20eats%20midday%20meals%20sitting%20cross-legged%20with%20the%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20they%20see%20me%20eating%20from%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20plate%20as%20theirs%2C%20they%20feel%20I%20am%20one%20of%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20seasonal%20fevers%2C%20she%20keeps%20basic%20medicines%20in%20the%20staffroom.%20%E2%80%9COn%20days%20when%20rice%20is%20served%20in%20the%20midday%20meal%2C%20I%20avoid%20giving%20it%20to%20sick%20children%2C%20as%20rice%20is%20believed%20to%20aggravate%20colds.%20Instead%2C%20I%20share%20my%20tiffin%20with%20them%20before%20giving%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20school%20day%20officially%20ends%20at%202%20PM%2C%20but%20the%20work%20continues%20%E2%80%94%20preparing%20lesson%20plans%2C%20completing%20paperwork%2C%20and%20visiting%20families%20whose%20children%20miss%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20true%20reward%20of%20teaching%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%